        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-14 14:08:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHow do we keep what you folks are doing in synch with our repo? It seems that you have copied a lot of the files over. I can foresee that policy will be updating these docker configuration files over the next 2 weeks. Especially with the updated policies.",
        "patchset_number": 1
