        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-14 14:18:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nLooks good to me, we need to address the forking of files from other components which is wide spread across OOM.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "1eb5b97514e47b64e2eea09f2bde09f2f9b3fff0",
        "author": {
